             G A M E    N O T E S    
                                                       
             
             "WE ARE THE VANGUARD OF HONOUR. THE CUTTING EDGE OF THE 
             BLOOD ANGELS. WE BRING DEATH." The legendary Space Hulk 
             returns to Windows PC, Mac and Linux in this epic turn 
             based strategy game. Set in the Warhammer 40,000 
             universe, an intriguing story of legendary battles and 
             heroic actions unfolds.
             
             Notes: Game is Multi6, DLCs are also included. You can
